Package org.ginsim.core.graph.hierarchicaltransitiongraph

Class HierarchicalNode

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.ginsim.core.graph.hierarchicaltransitiongraph.HierarchicalNode
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Comparable<Object>, Dotify
    public class HierarchicalNode
extends Object
implements Comparable<Object>, Dotify

    Define the nodes of the Hierarchical Transition Graph.

    A node has a unique id uid, a type defining the kind of Strongly Connected Component it contains and statesSet, the set of all the states it contains.

    Author:
    Duncan Berenguier
